column1: Project Title: ONION MAGGOT/STICKY TRAP PERFORMANCE TRIAL "COLOR" JUNE 2005
Document: ONION MAGGOT STICKY TRAP COLOR TRIAL 2005.docx

column2: Evaluate onion maggot fly attraction to spherical traps of different colors
Different color spheres were covered with sticky material and placed in the field in 2005.  Male and Female onion maggot stuck to the traps were evaluated

column1: Original document and project brief received from Brian Nault in late 2018, data entered into tabular form in this document May 7, 2019
